{
  "stem": "7624.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, somebody opens the door and puts a light on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were two gendarme with rifles and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "French-- and said, get dressed come with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't have much choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took me-- it was 3 or 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took me to a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were already a whole bunch of my friends there from the children home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also in the village, we had quite a few Jewish refugees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were also taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us in a bus and took us to a camp, [INAUDIBLE] [? was in it, ?] not far away from there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, I met some other people from the other children home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have four or five children home in the-- in that department there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would say we were about 150, 180 men in that, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Men, men and boys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I found out that anybody who is under 16-year-old will be released.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was one week under my 16th birthday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was released.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All my friends who were over 16 were deported and never came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you can imagine how--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How much thanks I had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were shipped to Drancy at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what Drancy was at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found out afterward.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When this happened, I know that it's time to do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jewish organization took me to a different children home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the law was that if you are working for agriculture, you still are OK.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They won't take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, they gave me papers say I'm working as agriculture in the farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was a--",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
